*

1. On je bio *iznenađen* što nije dobio pozivnicu. (He was surprised that he didn't receive an invitation.)
2. Ona je izgledala *iznenađeno* kada je čula vest. (She looked surprised when she heard the news.)
3. Oni su bili *iznenađeni* kada su videli ponudu. (They were surprised when they saw the offer.)
4. *Iznenađenje* je bilo ogromno kad su otkrili istinu. (The surprise was huge when they discovered the truth.)
5. Ja sam bio *iznenađen* kad su mi rekli da sam dobio posao. (I was surprised when they told me I got the job.)